The '''Imperial Taxation Bureau''' was the government body under [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] that was responsible for collecting taxes from [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] citizens, as well as setting tax rates.

